D \subset \mathbf{R}^2
f \in C^{(1)}(D)
f(x,y)\equiv \text{constant}
x\frac{\partial f(x,y)}{\partial x}+y\frac{\partial f(x,y)}{\partial y}=0, \left((x,y)\in D\right)
(x,y)\in D
f(x,y)=f(0,0)
t\in (0,1)
g
[0,1]
g:[0,1]\to \Bbb R,\quad g(t)=f(tx,ty).
t\cdot g'(t)=tx\cdot\frac{\partial f}{\partial x}(tx,ty)+ty\cdot\frac{\partial f}{\partial y}(tx,ty)=0\Longrightarrow g'(t)=0,
